reviewText: The peer review to complete the course is garbage. When stuff sits ignored in the review bin so students can't finish, that's a fail in course design, not in the students.I doubt I will ever get a certificate for this course, even though I did the work based on the lack of someone else completing a peer review. I keep extending the calendar on the course to no avail.
I have expected that GDPR and HIPPA will be explained/key items will be reviewed.
